<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
'''Merchandise''' is distributed by VRChat, and its partners. These products are VRChat-themed, and are physically made to order, and sometimes are limited.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Merchandise Lab ==
VRChat's current official outlet for merchandise is hosted on their "Merch Lab". It was launched<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-30-may-2024/24821 'Developer Update - 30 May 2024'] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref> on May 30, 2024, and includes an assortment of clothing and accessories. These products are also known as "VRChat Gear", stylized as ''VRCGEAR.''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* {{VRC link|https://hello.vrchat.com/merch-hub|VRChat Merch Hub}}
* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fZBAknQ5E44 VRC Hat & More - Get Yours Now!] promotional video on ''YouTube''.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Makeship ==
VRChat is partnered with Makeship to hold limited-time promotions on VRChat merchandise campaigns.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===VRCat plush===
[[File:VRCat Plushie.webp|thumb|VRChat's promotional banner for the VRCat plush.]]
VRChat's first product campaign with Makeship, was the VRCat plush. The campaign ran from December 9, 2021, and ended on January 7, 2022.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZBCVU8KrkOw VRCat Plushie] promotional video, on ''YouTube''.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
<blockquote>''The world hopping feli- meow!! ... feline is ready to land in reality! The first of many "physicals" to pop out of VRChat.''
''Meowww!''
''Pat its head, plop it in front of a mir- MEOW ... mirror, or just place it in your play space so it can watch you dance in your HMD.''
''Meeeeeoooowwww! Meow!''
''Would someone just please take this cat away from- meow!?!''</blockquote>
</div>


<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Size and material===
* Height: 16.0cm
* Materials: Polypropylene cotton, plush fabric (ultra-soft fleece)
''Some lengths and/or widths may vary based on specific character pose.''<ref>[https://www.makeship.com/products/vrcat-plush VRCat Plush] on Makeship; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref>
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===VRCat vinyl figurine===
[[File:VRCat Vinyl.jpg|thumb|Promotional image of the VRCat vinyl figurine.]]
VRChat's second product campaign with Makeship, was a vinyl figurine of VRCat. This campaign ran from November 17 to December 9, 2023.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
