<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==EOZ==
EOZ is a company that creates body straps for [[Special:MyLanguage/Full-Body Tracking|full-body tracking]] (FBT) peripherals. EOZ partnered with VRChat, and some VRChat communities such as [[Special:MyLanguage/Community:Trans Academy|Trans Academy]]<ref>[https://www.eozvr.com/products/ta-x-eoz Trans Academy X EOZ Straps] on EOZ's website; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref> and SHELTERCON<ref>[https://www.eozvr.com/products/shelter-v-limited-edition SHELTERCON X EOZ Straps] on EOZ's website; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref> to create full body tracking straps. Tundra Labs also distributes these EOZ straps.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
*[https://www.eozvr.com/ EOZ website] on ''eozvr.com''
*[https://www.eozvr.com/products/vrchat-x-eoz VRChat X EOZ V2 Straps] on EOZ's website on ''eozvr.com''
**[https://tundra-labs.com/products/vrchat-x-eoz-fullbody-tracking-straps-v2 VRChat X EOZ V2 Straps] on Tundra Labs' website on ''tundra-labs.com''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Bigscreen ==
Bigscreen is a company which develops VR software and hardware.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Bigscreen Beyond x VRChat Storage Can ===
The [https://store.bigscreenvr.com/products/bigscreen-beyond-x-vrchat-storage-can Bigscreen Beyond x VRChat Storage Can] is a storage container which is designed to store the Bigscreen Beyond headset. This counterpart features VRChat branding and design elements around the can. This limited edition storage can was announced on February 6, 2024,<ref>[https://x.com/BigscreenVR/status/1754942807616454759 Excited to unveil the Bigscreen Beyond Storage Can] on X; retrieved July 17, 2025.</ref> and marks the first collaboration between VRChat and Bigscreen.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition ===
The Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition is a limited edition version of the Bigscreen Beyond 2e headset. This edition includes the base Bigscreen Beyond 2e headset, along with exclusive bonuses that are in-box and on VRChat. These exclusive bonuses are:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* "Atomic Purple" Cover Shell
* "Custom box" which is VRChat themed packaging for the headset
* "Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition Owner" [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]]
* "[[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers#Bigscreen|Seeing Beyond]]" [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|sticker]]
* "[[Special:MyLanguage/Items#List of items|Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition]]" [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|item]]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
This limited edition Bigscreen Beyond 2e was announced on July 16, 2025,<ref>[https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/announcing-the-bigscreen-beyond-2-vrchat-edition Announcing the Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition!] on ''hello.vrchat.com''; retrieved July 17, 2025.</ref> and marks the second collaboration between VRChat and Bigscreen.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== NEO4IC ==
[[File:Neo4ic promo.webp|thumb|Official promotion for VRChat x NEO4IC "Tree of Realms" collaboration shirt for New Years Eve 2023.]]
NEO4IC (pronounced ''"neo-phoric"'') is a company that creates techwear clothing and accessories. For the [[Special:MyLanguage/New Years Eve|New Years Eve]] 2023 event, VRChat partnered with NEO4IC to release a collaboration t-shirt<ref>[https://neo4ic.com/products/vrchat-tree-of-realms VRChat Tree of Realms] on ''neo4ic.com''; retrieved December 7, 2024.</ref>, dubbed the "Tree of Realms". NEO4IC was given a collaboration booth inside the New Years Eve 2023 event world.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
NEO4IC has also partnered with SHELTERCON<ref>[https://neo4ic.com/products/shelter-v5? SHELTER V5 shirt] on ''neo4ic.com''; retrieved December 7, 2024.</ref><ref>[https://neo4ic.com/collections/mens/products/shelter-hoodie SHELTERCON Hoodie] on ''neo4ic.com''; retrieved December 7, 2024.</ref> for merchandise.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
On the January 19, 2023 [[Special:MyLanguage/Developer Update|Developer Update]], there was announcement<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-19-january-2023 'Developer Update' - 19 January 2023] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; retrieved December 7, 2024.</ref> regarding Tree of Realms shirts left to be sold. As of February 2023, all stock was sold out.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
<blockquote>''"We are honored to have the chance to collaborate with virtual realities largest and most active social platform: VRChat.''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
''We have joined forces with their team to produce their official NYE event shirt - that will be accessed in the custom world or online."''</blockquote>
</div>

